-- Colombia's New Government Won't Sell Power Company Isagen, Zuluaga Says
-- Helen Murphy
-- 2010-07-02T13:23:01Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-02/colombia-s-new-government-won-t-sell-power-company-isagen-zuluaga-says.html

          
          
             Colombia Finance Minister Oscar Ivan
Zuluaga said that the goverment has scrapped plans to sell its
stake in state-controlled power company Isagen Sa.  
